{"root":{"data":{"id":"dbjx3yvppi80","created":1753322939614,"text":"渲染框架"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbjx43obmmg0","created":1753322950051,"text":"Linux"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbjx4g0ctiw0","created":1753322976900,"text":"x11","note":"绘制一条线的过程可以概括为：\n\n1. 应用程序调用 XDrawLine，通过网络协议发送绘图请求。\n\n2. X 服务器接收请求，进行光栅化，确定要改变哪些像素。\n\n3. 驱动程序将光栅化结果写入显存中的帧缓冲区。\n\n4. 显卡读取帧缓冲区内容，将其显示在屏幕上。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dc1u5yazjpk0","created":1755142710979,"text":"skia"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dc1u61bv5eo0","created":1755142717563,"text":"cairo"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbjx4hgflgg0","created":1753322980049,"text":"Wayland"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbjx47txz680","created":1753322959098,"text":"Windows","note":"应用层 ─┬─ Win32 API (传统窗口)\n        ├─ UWP/XAML (现代应用)\n        └─ DirectX API (游戏、高性能图形)\n\n中间层 ─┬─ DirectComposition (合成引擎)\n        └─ Direct2D/Direct3D (渲染引擎)\n\n驱动层 ─┬─ D3D 驱动 (GPU 加速)\n        └─ WDDM (Windows 显示驱动模型)\n\n硬件层 ── GPU/显示设备\n\n\n"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbjx7pgz6aw0","created":1753323232589,"text":"GDI"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbjx7qnlxu00","created":1753323235166,"text":"DirectX"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbjx7tfj8ew0","created":1753323241208,"text":"D2D"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbjx7vs10z40","created":1753323246317,"text":"D3D"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbjx7xhk4t40","created":1753323250038,"text":"DirectComposition"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbjx82zbyvc0","created":1753323261997,"text":"OpenGL"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbjx495ooso0","created":1753322961985,"text":"MacOS"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbjxkwml2l40","created":1753324266899,"text":"Metal","note":"\n自研的低级别图像API。通过IoKit驱动屏蔽不同GPU差异\n\n是macos/ios/ipados的核心渲染基础\n\n上层应用提供了 `AppKit` 和 `SwiftUI` 提供应用层接口"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbjxiehdocw0","created":1753324070674,"text":"Core Graphics(Quartz 2D)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbjxirealr40","created":1753324098786,"text":"Core Animation"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbjxitjy7og0","created":1753324103481,"text":"Quartz Compositor"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbjx4brd7m00","created":1753322967649,"text":"Android"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dc0hor77qxs0","created":1755005950047,"text":"跨平台UI框架"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dc0hp366i8w0","created":1755005976106,"text":"React native"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}